data.description: Gorgeous all brick home with a 2 car attached garage and metal roof located on a nice 1.3 acre lot. House has a large open floor plan with an eat in kitchen that has all new  stainless steel appliances.  Spacious living room with fresh paint throughout the house. It also has a large rec/bonus room above the garage with a full bathroom that could be used as a extra bedroom. Outside is an RV carport with RV/camper hookup and a beautiful gazebo right next to the carport.  Home is just 2 minutes from the local golf course. NEWLY INSTALLED 6 PERSON STORM  SHELTER AS WELL. The outdoor building under the RV carport, washer and dryer and curtains and the black temporary  fence do not convey.  Great opportunity!!
